---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="&LAB TOKYO | ローフード・発酵料理教室 東京・渋谷"
  description="東京・渋谷のローフード・発酵料理教室 &LAB TOKYO。ELLE gourmet認定料理家・安藤千英が主宰。ローショコラティエ協会本部。JLBAローフードマイスター・発酵プランナー・ローチョコレートマイスター養成講座。"
  canonical="https://www.andlabtokyo.com/"
  type="website"
>

<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100svh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  background: #1A1715;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 80px 24px 60px;
}
.hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url('https://static.wixstatic.com/media/745f65_7c4c8d79025e432e8a9bd02e8dc3a455~mv2.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  opacity: 0.35;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  position: relative;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #C6A15B;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero-title {
  position: relative;
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 200;
  color: #FAF5EC;
  line-height: 1.3;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.hero-title-en {
  position: relative;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 22px);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #C0B6A8;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.hero-rule {
  position: relative;
  width: 40px;
  height: 1px;
  background: #C6A15B;
  margin: 0 auto 28px;
}
.hero-desc {
  position: relative;
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: clamp(13px, 1.5vw, 16px);
  color: #C0B6A8;
  line-height: 2;
  max-width: 520px;
  margin: 0 auto 40px;
}
.hero-btns {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
}
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #C6A15B;
  color: #1A1715;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 14px 32px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #A8865A; }
.btn-outline {
  display: inline-block;
  border: 1px solid rgba(198,161,91,0.5);
  color: #C6A15B;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 13px 28px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}
.btn-outline:hover { border-color: #C6A15B; color: #FAF5EC; }

/* ===== SECTION SHARED ===== */
.sec { padding: 80px 24px; }
.inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.sec-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #8C7A6A;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.sec-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 38px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #1C1C1A;
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.sec-rule {
  width: 32px;
  height: 1px;
  background: #8C7A6A;
  margin: 16px 0 28px;
}
.sec-lead {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #5A5A58;
  line-height: 2;
  max-width: 660px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

/* ===== NUMBERS ===== */
.about-sec { background: #FAF9F6; }
.numbers {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.number-item {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 120px;
  background: #fff;
  padding: 28px 20px;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(28,28,26,0.05);
}
.number-val {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 54px);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1C1C1A;
  line-height: 1;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.number-label {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: #8C7A6A;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

/* ===== COURSES GRID ===== */
.courses-sec { background: #1C1C1A; }
.courses-sec .sec-eyebrow { color: #A8865A; }
.courses-sec .sec-title { color: #FAF5EC; }
.courses-sec .sec-rule { background: #A8865A; }
.courses-sec .sec-lead { color: #C0B6A8; }

.courses-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
}
.course-card {
  background: #24211E;
  padding: 32px 28px;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
  transition: background 0.2s;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
}
.course-card:hover { background: #2C2926; border-bottom-color: #C6A15B; }
.course-card-tag {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #C6A15B;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.course-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: #FAF5EC;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.course-card p {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #C0B6A8;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.courses-more {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

/* ===== RAWCHOCOLATIER BAND ===== */
.rawchoco-sec {
  background: #110E0B;
  padding: 80px 24px;
  text-align: center;
}
.rawchoco-sec .sec-eyebrow { color: #A8865A; }
.rawchoco-sec .sec-title { color: #FAF5EC; text-align: center; }
.rawchoco-sec .sec-lead { color: #C0B6A8; margin: 0 auto 40px; text-align: center; }
.rawchoco-links {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.rawchoco-link {
  display: inline-block;
  border: 1px solid rgba(198,161,91,0.3);
  color: #C6A15B;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}
.rawchoco-link:hover { background: #C6A15B; color: #110E0B; }

/* ===== KNOWLEDGE ===== */
.knowledge-sec { background: #FAF9F6; }
.knowledge-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
}
.knowledge-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid rgba(28,28,26,0.06);
  padding: 28px 24px;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.knowledge-card:hover { border-color: #8C7A6A; }
.knowledge-card-en {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #8C7A6A;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.knowledge-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: #1C1C1A;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.knowledge-card p {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #6A6A68;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.knowledge-more {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 36px;
}
.btn-text {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #3C3C3A;
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28,28,26,0.2);
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.btn-text:hover { border-color: #1C1C1A; }

/* ===== ABOUT / PROFILE ===== */
.profile-sec {
  background: #1C1C1A;
  padding: 80px 24px;
}
.profile-inner {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: center;
}
.profile-img {
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  background: #24211E;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.profile-img img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.profile-text .sec-eyebrow { color: #A8865A; }
.profile-text .sec-title { color: #FAF5EC; font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 30px); }
.profile-text .sec-rule { background: #A8865A; }
.profile-name-en {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #C6A15B;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: block;
}
.profile-text p {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #C0B6A8;
  line-height: 2;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.profile-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin: 20px 0;
}
.profile-tag {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: #A8865A;
  border: 1px solid rgba(168,134,90,0.35);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

/* ===== CTA ===== */
.cta-sec {
  background: #C6A15B;
  padding: 72px 24px;
  text-align: center;
}
.cta-sec h2 {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 32px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #1A1715;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.cta-sec p {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(26,23,21,0.7);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.btn-dark {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #1A1715;
  color: #FAF5EC;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  padding: 14px 36px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.btn-dark:hover { background: #3C3C3A; }

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .courses-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .knowledge-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .profile-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .profile-img { max-width: 360px; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .courses-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .knowledge-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .numbers { flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <span class="hero-eyebrow">Tokyo · Shibuya</span>
  <h1 class="hero-title">&LAB TOKYO</h1>
  <p class="hero-title-en">Raw Food &amp; Fermentation School</p>
  <div class="hero-rule"></div>
  <p class="hero-desc">
    ローフード・発酵・植物性食材の可能性を探求する、<br>
    東京・渋谷の料理教室 &amp;ラボ トーキョー。<br>
    JLBA認定ローフードマイスター、ローショコラティエ協会本部。
  </p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="/listofcourses" class="btn-primary">全講座を見る</a>
    <a href="/experiencelessons" class="btn-outline">体験レッスン</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== ABOUT NUMBERS ===== -->
<section class="sec about-sec">
  <div class="inner">
    <span class="sec-eyebrow">About &amp;LAB TOKYO</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title">食の本質を、<br>自分の手で学ぶ場所</h2>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
    <p class="sec-lead">2015年の開講以来、ローフード・発酵・ロースイーツ・スピルリナなど、食の最前線をテーマに多彩な講座を展開。ELLE gourmet認定料理家・安藤千英が主宰する、プロも通う本格的な料理教室です。</p>

    <div class="numbers">
      <div class="number-item">
        <span class="number-val">2015</span>
        <span class="number-label">設立年</span>
      </div>
      <div class="number-item">
        <span class="number-val">500<small style="font-size:0.5em">+</small></span>
        <span class="number-label">年間受講生</span>
      </div>
      <div class="number-item">
        <span class="number-val">50<small style="font-size:0.5em">+</small></span>
        <span class="number-label">講座・メニュー数</span>
      </div>
      <div class="number-item">
        <span class="number-val">10<small style="font-size:0.5em">+</small></span>
        <span class="number-label">取得可能資格</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center">
      <a href="/brand" class="btn-text">&amp;LAB TOKYO について詳しく →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== COURSES ===== -->
<section class="sec courses-sec">
  <div class="inner">
    <span class="sec-eyebrow">Courses</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title">各種講座</h2>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
    <p class="sec-lead">初心者から、資格取得・プロ養成まで。あなたのステージに合わせた多彩な講座をご用意しています。</p>

    <div class="courses-grid">
      <a href="/experiencelessons" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">Trial</span>
        <h3>体験レッスン</h3>
        <p>初めての方でも気軽に参加できる体験レッスン。ローフードや発酵の世界を楽しく体験。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rawfood-kentei-meister" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">Certification · JLBA</span>
        <h3>ローフードマイスター講座</h3>
        <p>JLBA国際認定の資格が取得できる本格講座。酵素・栄養学から実践レシピまで体系的に学ぶ。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/fermentedfood" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">Fermentation</span>
        <h3>発酵プランナー講座</h3>
        <p>塩麹・甘酒・味噌・ぬか漬けなど、日本の伝統発酵食を深く学ぶ専門講座。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rawchocolatier/rawchocolatemeister" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">Raw Chocolate</span>
        <h3>ローチョコレートマイスター養成講座</h3>
        <p>ローショコラティエ協会認定。カカオの世界とローチョコレートの本格技術を習得。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rawchocolatier/rawpatissier" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">Raw Sweets</span>
        <h3>ローパティシエ養成講座</h3>
        <p>ロースイーツの理論と実践を体系的に学ぶ。プロとしての活動を目指す方に。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/koji-fermentation-experience-tokyo" class="course-card">
        <span class="course-card-tag">KOJI LAB</span>
        <h3>UMAMI &amp; KOJI LAB</h3>
        <p>英語で学ぶ麹の文化とUMAMIの科学。外国からのゲストにも対応。</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="courses-more">
      <a href="/listofcourses" class="btn-outline" style="border-color:rgba(198,161,91,0.4);color:#C6A15B">全講座一覧を見る →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== RAWCHOCOLATIER ASSOCIATION ===== -->
<section class="rawchoco-sec">
  <span class="sec-eyebrow">Association</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 12px">ローショコラティエ協会</h2>
  <div class="sec-rule" style="margin:16px auto 24px"></div>
  <p class="sec-lead">ローチョコレート・ロースイーツに特化した世界初の協会。登録商標「ローショコラティエ®」「ローパティシエ®」のもと、プロフェッショナルを育成。</p>
  <div class="rawchoco-links">
    <a href="/rawchocolatier/rawchocolatier-course" class="rawchoco-link">ローショコラティエ</a>
    <a href="/rawchocolatier/rawchocolateconcierge" class="rawchoco-link">ローチョコレートコンシェルジュ</a>
    <a href="/rawchocolatier/online-lesson" class="rawchoco-link">オンラインレッスン</a>
    <a href="/rawchocolatier/about-association" class="rawchoco-link">協会概要</a>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:36px">
    <a href="/rawchocolatier" class="btn-primary">協会トップへ</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== KNOWLEDGE ===== -->
<section class="sec knowledge-sec">
  <div class="inner">
    <span class="sec-eyebrow">Knowledge</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title">食の知識を深める</h2>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
    <p class="sec-lead">ローフード・発酵・ローチョコレートなど、&LAB TOKYOが専門とする食のジャンルについて詳しく解説します。</p>

    <div class="knowledge-grid">
      <a href="/rawfood" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Raw Food</span>
        <h3>ローフードとは</h3>
        <p>加熱しない食事法で酵素を活かす、ローフードの基礎知識。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/fermentedfood" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Fermentation</span>
        <h3>発酵とは</h3>
        <p>腸活・免疫・旨味。日本の発酵食文化の奥深さを解説。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/livingfood" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Living Food</span>
        <h3>リビングフードとは</h3>
        <p>生きた食材の力を最大限に活かす、リビングフードの考え方。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rawchocolatier/rawchocolate" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Raw Chocolate</span>
        <h3>ローチョコレートとは</h3>
        <p>非加熱で作るローチョコレートの製法と栄養価。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rawchocolatier/whatrawsweets" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Raw Sweets</span>
        <h3>ロースイーツとは</h3>
        <p>砂糖・乳製品・小麦粉不使用。自然素材のみで作るスイーツ。</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/spirulina" class="knowledge-card">
        <span class="knowledge-card-en">Spirulina</span>
        <h3>スピルリナとは</h3>
        <p>50以上の栄養素を含むスーパーフード、スピルリナの全て。</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="knowledge-more">
      <a href="/knowledge" class="btn-text">ナレッジ一覧を見る →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PROFILE ===== -->
<section class="profile-sec">
  <div class="profile-inner">
    <div class="profile-img">
      <img
        src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/745f65_e3e2cfcf4e2f416e80c49a57b7f6eaf2~mv2.jpg"
        alt="安藤千英 / Chie Ando"
        loading="lazy"
        onerror="this.parentElement.style.background='#24211E'"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="profile-text">
      <span class="sec-eyebrow">Founder</span>
      <h2 class="sec-title">安藤千英</h2>
      <div class="sec-rule"></div>
      <span class="profile-name-en">Chie Ando</span>
      <div class="profile-tags">
        <span class="profile-tag">ELLE gourmet 認定料理家</span>
        <span class="profile-tag">JLBAアンバサダー</span>
        <span class="profile-tag">ローショコラティエ協会代表</span>
        <span class="profile-tag">発酵プランナー</span>
      </div>
      <p>ローフード・発酵・プランツベースの食を専門とする料理家。2015年に&LAB TOKYOを設立し、これまでに延べ500名以上の受講生を指導。</p>
      <p>書籍監修・企業レシピ開発・メディア出演など、幅広い分野で活躍。</p>
